query:
INSERT INTO tuitionFees (programId, academicYear, amountPerYear, currency, paymentSchedule, notes) 
SELECT 
  p.id,
  '2024-2025',
  25000,
  'GBP',
  'per_year',
  'International student fees for MBA'
FROM programs p WHERE p.nameEn = 'Master of Business Administration' AND p.universityId = (SELECT id FROM universities WHERE nameEn = 'Imperial College London')
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  p.id,
  '2024-2025',
  22000,
  'GBP',
  'per_year',
  'International student fees for MSc Computer Science'
FROM programs p WHERE p.nameEn = 'Master of Computer Science' AND p.universityId = (SELECT id FROM universities WHERE nameEn = 'Imperial College London')
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  p.id,
  '2024-2025',
  18000,
  'CHF',
  'per_year',
  'International student fees for Bachelor Engineering'
FROM programs p WHERE p.nameEn = 'Bachelor of Engineering' AND p.universityId = (SELECT id FROM universities WHERE nameEn = 'ETH Zurich')
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  p.id,
  '2024-2025',
  0,
  'CHF',
  'per_year',
  'PhD programs are fully funded'
FROM programs p WHERE p.nameEn = 'PhD in Physics' AND p.universityId = (SELECT id FROM universities WHERE nameEn = 'ETH Zurich')
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  p.id,
  '2024-2025',
  28000,
  'GBP',
  'per_year',
  'International student fees for MSc Finance'
FROM programs p WHERE p.nameEn = 'Master of Finance' AND p.universityId = (SELECT id FROM universities WHERE nameEn = 'The London School of Economics and Political Science');
